{"tid":2099974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★譚仔調景嶺彩明分店有員工家屬確診","createTime":"2020-07-08T16:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T17:08:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"05c77f95492610bbf68351d2005a148ada43b90a","tid":2099974,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"譚仔雲南米線今日（8日）發聲明指，得悉彩明分店一名員工的家屬確診新型冠狀病毒肺炎，該員工已兩日無上班，全店員工將需隔離14日後才可上班，而涉事的分店即日起停業三日，至周六（11日）重開，屆時將安排其他分店健康狀況良好的員工為顧客服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/495667/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AD%9A%E4%BB%94%E8%AA%BF%E6%99%AF%E5%B6%BA%E5%BD%A9%E6%98%8E%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97%E6%9C%89%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A5%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F495667%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25AD%259A%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%2599%25AF%25E5%25B6%25BA%25E5%25BD%25A9%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=871f0184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/495667/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AD%9A%E4%BB%94%E8%AA%BF%E6%99%AF%E5%B6%BA%E5%BD%A9%E6%98%8E%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97%E6%9C%89%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A5%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2</a>"},{"pid":"49ff078df040c45e0e58aa6133e864c09ca368d3","tid":2099974,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/